---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About Us - The Travel Backpack"
  description="Learn about The Travel Backpack — our mission to help travelers find the best gear, backpacks, and travel tips for every adventure."
  canonical="https://thetravelbackpack.com/about-us/"
>
  <div class="py-12">
    <div class="container-custom max-w-4xl">
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-8">About The Travel Backpack</h1>

      <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 mb-8">
          We're passionate travelers and gear enthusiasts dedicated to helping you find the perfect backpack for every adventure.
        </p>

        <h2>Our Mission</h2>
        <p>
          The Travel Backpack was created to cut through the noise of generic gear reviews. We research, compare,
          and test backpacks so you can make confident buying decisions — whether you're a weekend hiker, a digital
          nomad, or a student heading to campus.
        </p>

        <h2>What We Cover</h2>
        <ul>
          <li>In-depth backpack reviews across every category and price range</li>
          <li>Travel packing guides and checklists</li>
          <li>Gear comparisons and buyer's guides</li>
          <li>Tips for traveling light and smart</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>Our Values</h2>
        <p>
          We believe in honest, unbiased recommendations. When we include affiliate links, we disclose it clearly —
          and we only recommend products we'd genuinely use ourselves. Your trust matters more than any commission.
        </p>

        <h2>Get in Touch</h2>
        <p>
          Have a question, a backpack you'd like us to review, or just want to say hello?
          <a href="/contact-us/">Contact us here</a>.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
